    "name": "NIST National Vulnerability Database (NVD) API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "The National Vulnerability Database (NVD) API, operated by the National Institute of Standards and Technology, provides programmatic access to Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE) records, CVE change history, and Common Platform Enumeration (CPE) records. The API supports pagination, filtering, and date-range queries for vulnerability and product data.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: NIST NVD",
